name: It's a Small World
description: This was my first attempt at level construction, so don't give me any crap. I didn't think it was all that good myself, but a guy I Deathmatch with liked it, so here it is. It's very simple, good for Deathmatch newbies. Just a couple of courtyards, a dark room, a VERY dark hallway, and a couple of surprises.
